name: Ex1: Testing Sing Up with wrong symbols in email

steps.name: Press Give Allow Bluetooth button on welcome screen
Checking intro text on welcome screen
Swipe right for read all welcome info
Press "Sign Up" button on welcome screen
Click on "'#fake_email.com'" field", clear and set app email for IOS or Android
Check email error text is visible
